<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Interview Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 1.5em;
    }
    p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    ul {
      padding: 0;
      list-style-type: none;
    }
    ul li {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #007bff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }
    a.reject {
      background-color: #dc3545;
    }
    a:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Interview Invitation</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= first_name %> <%= last_name %>,</p>
    <p>You have been invited for an interview for the <strong><%= job_title %></strong> position at <strong><%= job_company %></strong>.</p>

    <h2>Interview Details:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Date and Time:</strong> <%= formatDate(proposed_time) %></li>
      <li><strong>Format:</strong> <%= is_online ? 'Online' : 'On-site' %></li>
      <% if (!is_online) { %>
        <li><strong>City:</strong> <%= city %></li>
        <li><strong>Street Address:</strong> <%= street_address %></li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>

    <p>Please confirm your attendance by clicking one of the links below:</p>
    <p>
      <a href="<%= confirm_link %>">Confirm Attendance</a>
      <a href="<%= reject_link %>" class="reject">Reject Invitation</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out. We look forward to meeting you!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
